			Profile
			
			



Dr.&nbsp;YangXu,&nbsp;AssociateProfessor(Ph.D.advisor)
Education:
U.ofIllinoisatUrbanaandChampaigninECE,USA&nbsp;Ph.D.&nbsp;&nbsp;
U.ofIllinoisatUrbanaandChampaigninECE,USA&nbsp;M.S.&nbsp;&nbsp;
TsinghuaUniversity,Beijing,ChinainECE,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;B.S.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;




























&nbsp;&nbsp;Myresearchinterestsincludemodeling,multiphysicsanalysis,andfabricationofnano-/microelectromechanicalsystems(NEMS/MEMS),nanoelectronicdevices,andnext-generationICcircuits.
&nbsp;&nbsp;Our&nbsp;researchlab,withEnglish-friendlyacademicenvironment,&nbsp;nowhasseveralinternational&nbsp;Ph.D.&nbsp;students.Weestablishedlong-termresearchcollaborationwithHarvard,Stanford,UIUC,UCBerkeley,Cornell,UCLA,ColumbiaUniversity,USC,andNYU.&nbsp;InternationalstudentsarewelcometojoinourresearchteamforMasterandDoctoralDegrees.


