&nbsp;&nbsp;Outstandingpreviousgraduates&nbsp;continuetheirhighereduationatIvyLeagueuniversityforPh.Ddegreesorareworkingat&nbsp;well-knownenterprisessuchasIntel,IBM,AMD,Motorola,Apple,ChinaMobile,ChinaTelecom,etc.
